<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Master Model Release – LumenNyx Studios</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />

  <style>
    .wrap { max-width: 980px; margin: 1.5rem auto 2rem auto; padding: 0 1.25rem; }
    .block { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10); border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.2rem; }
    .muted { color:#9aa0b5; font-size:0.92rem; }
    .mono { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono","Courier New", monospace; font-size:0.88rem; word-break: break-word; }
    .legal h4 { margin-top: 1.2rem; }
    .legal p { margin: 0.45rem 0; line-height: 1.45; }
    .summary-box { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 12px; padding: 0.9rem; }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="home">

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="site-header-inner">
    <a href="/model/profile" class="brand-link">
      <span class="brand-mark"><img src="/img/lumennyx-mark.png" alt="LumenNyx logo"></span>
      <span class="brand-text">LUMENNYX STUDIOS</span>
    </a>

    <nav class="main-nav">
      <a href="/model/profile" class="active">Model Portal</a>
      <a href="/model/scenes">My Scenes</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
      <a href="/2257">2257</a>
      <form action="/logout" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
        <button class="btn secondary" style="padding:0.25rem 0.9rem;font-size:0.8rem;">Logout</button>
      </form>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="wrap">

  <% if (message) { %>
    <div class="alert success"><%= message %></div>
  <% } %>
  <% if (error) { %>
    <div class="alert error"><%= error %></div>
  <% } %>

  <section class="portal-section">
    <h2>Master Model Release & Performance Agreement</h2>
    <p class="portal-note">
      This is the studio’s general, legally binding master agreement.
      Scene-specific boundaries, acts, partners, and limits are handled separately
      via consent &amp; safety forms or written addenda.
    </p>

    <div class="block legal">

      <!-- ============================= -->
      <!-- BINDING LEGAL AGREEMENT TEXT -->
      <!-- ============================= -->

      <h4>1. Identification & Age Verification</h4>
      <p>
        The undersigned performer (“Performer”) represents and warrants that they are at least
        eighteen (18) years of age and of legal capacity to enter into this Agreement.
        Performer affirms that all identification documents submitted to LumenNyx Studios
        (“Studio”) are accurate, authentic, and belong to Performer.
      </p>

      <h4>2. Voluntary Participation & Capacity</h4>
      <p>
        Performer confirms participation is voluntary and free from coercion, impairment,
        or duress. Performer understands the nature of adult content production and
        affirms the legal capacity to enter this Agreement.
      </p>

      <h4>3. Grant of Rights</h4>
      <p>
        Performer irrevocably grants Studio and its licensees the right to photograph,
        record, reproduce, edit, distribute, publish, transmit, display, license, and
        otherwise exploit Performer’s image, likeness, voice, name(s), and performance
        in any media now known or later developed, worldwide, in perpetuity,
        subject only to written limitations expressly agreed and signed by both parties.
      </p>

      <h4>4. Compensation Acknowledgment</h4>
      <p>
        Performer acknowledges that compensation terms may be set per project or addendum.
        Unless expressly stated in writing, Performer is not entitled to royalties or residuals.
      </p>

      <h4>5. Independent Contractor Status</h4>
      <p>
        Performer is an independent contractor and not an employee of Studio.
        Performer is solely responsible for taxes, filings, and insurance.
      </p>

      <h4>6. Assumption of Risk</h4>
      <p>
        Performer acknowledges that participation may involve physical exertion and
        voluntarily assumes all lawful risks associated with agreed performance activities.
      </p>

      <h4>7. Waiver of Inspection & Approval</h4>
      <p>
        Performer waives any right to inspect or approve final content, titles, edits,
        or promotional materials, provided Performer is not materially misrepresented.
      </p>

      <h4>8. Internet & Distribution Disclaimer</h4>
      <p>
        Performer understands that once content is distributed, complete removal
        from the internet cannot be guaranteed due to third-party redistribution or piracy.
      </p>

      <h4>9. Release of Liability & Indemnification</h4>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, Performer releases Studio from claims
        arising from authorized use under this Agreement and agrees to indemnify Studio
        for losses caused by Performer’s breach of representations.
      </p>

      <h4>10. Governing Law & Venue</h4>
      <p>
        This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the State of New York,
        with venue in New York state or federal courts.
      </p>

      <h4>11. Electronic Signature & Metadata</h4>
      <p>
        Performer agrees that electronic execution constitutes a valid signature.
        The system records date, time, IP address, and user-agent as evidence of execution.
      </p>

      <!-- ============================= -->
      <!-- NON-BINDING SUMMARY -->
      <!-- ============================= -->

      <hr style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.10); margin: 1.2rem 0;" />

      <div class="summary-box">
        <h4 style="margin-top:0;">Plain-Language Summary (Non-Binding)</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>You confirm you are 18+ and your ID is real.</li>
          <li>You are participating voluntarily.</li>
          <li>The studio can record and distribute agreed content.</li>
          <li>Payment terms may vary by shoot.</li>
          <li>You are an independent contractor.</li>
          <li>Full internet removal cannot be guaranteed.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="muted">
          This summary is for convenience only. The legal agreement above controls.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ============================= -->
      <!-- SIGNATURE STATUS -->
      <!-- ============================= -->

      <hr style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.10); margin: 1.2rem 0;" />

      <h4>Signature Status</h4>
      <% if (masterRelease) { %>
        <p>
          <strong>On file:</strong>
          Signed as <em><%= masterRelease.signed_name %></em>
          on <%= masterRelease.signed_at %>.
        </p>
        <p class="mono">
          IP: <%= masterRelease.ip_address || '—' %><br/>
          User-Agent: <%= masterRelease.user_agent || '—' %>
        </p>
        <p class="muted">
          Re-signing will add a new record; prior signatures may be retained for audit purposes.
        </p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> Not signed yet.</p>
      <% } %>

      <!-- ============================= -->
      <!-- SIGNATURE FORM -->
      <!-- ============================= -->

      <form action="/model/release" method="POST" class="portal-form" style="margin-top:1rem;">

        <label class="checkbox-label">
          <input type="checkbox" name="agree_master_release" required />
          I confirm I am at least 18 years old and agree this is a legally binding contract.
        </label>

        <label class="checkbox-label">
          <input type="checkbox" required />
          I consent to electronic signature and metadata recording.
        </label>

        <label>
          Type your full legal name as your digital signature *
          <input type="text" name="signed_name" required placeholder="Full legal name" />
        </label>

        <button type="submit" class="btn primary">
          <%= masterRelease ? 'Re-Sign Master Release' : 'Sign Master Release' %>
        </button>

        <div style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
          <a class="btn secondary" href="/model/profile#release">Back to Profile</a>
        </div>
      </form>

    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
